{"tid":697873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： 的士行樓梯　唔上唔落","createTime":"2018-06-11T08:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T12:08:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1deb722595533250efc27410e979e1698a9e5540","tid":697873,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T08:44:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180611/20417114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F20417114&d=GbEA7B6eLkiPEXlQfMrUt7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=9d41cbff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F20417114&h=1dc40027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180611/20417114</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月11日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n的士行樓梯　唔上唔落<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180611/large/a1104a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180611%2Flarge%2Fa1104a.gif&h=7bea5290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有網民上載兩張疑似貪快的士「掛車」樓梯嘅相，可見車尾懸空進退不得。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為咗快，可以去到幾盡？有網民前晚喺fb上載兩張相，地址相信係葵涌業成街盡頭嘅行人樓梯，可以見到一架巿區的士車頭朝下，車尾呈半懸空狀態，前半車身已經駛咗入樓梯範圍。<br />\n<br />\n不過相信司機大佬發現如果一直駛落去，可能會失控炒車，最終停車熄匙。相中見車廂空無一人，估計司機已經離開現場，或者去咗搵人救車。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩張相曝光後，引發網民熱列討論，唔少人訕笑的士大佬呢個舉動，係打算走捷徑開快車，笑言：「最快由業成街去大連排道嘅方法，識揸一定咁揸！」上載者亦不禁引用廣告名句：「哼！用愛膚堅啦！」暗指司機可能香港腳發作肇禍。<br />\n<br />\n翻查地圖，如果依照呢個司機嘅駕駛路線，由業成街走樓梯落大連排道只需84米，但倒車出青山公路再轉入葵涌道，就要近2公里先可抵達大連排道，有網民估計司機貪快惹禍。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 巴士流血　惹藏屍疑雲<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 爆粗叔「掹槍」大鬧食店<br />\n<br />\n________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=T_ie47RK7xA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT_ie47RK7xA&d=GbEA7B6eLkiPEXlQfMrUt7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7ef3ce81\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=T_ie47RK7xA</a>"},{"pid":"9b4529c49609f03cadbe4b9a9dd1e5d76fb3d309","tid":697873,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:11:27.000Z","msg":"諗起牛唔飲水，唔行得後樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84412f705064d9f5510b122dffee0e5abff37356","tid":697873,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6feb160fe5c98d69bf1ef2886640a33590ea51d1","tid":697873,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港都出現呢啲on9事<br />\n真係回歸喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8bb72438ff48083b9d2a59df402918bb39ce4b9","tid":697873,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:16:27.000Z","msg":"當自己係四驅車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3775cff8ad130a15d27b12f3814cabc3aba3d874","tid":697873,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:16:49.000Z","msg":"做落咗去, 做咩唔落埋? 係就去盡啲, 垃圾的士佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54474ad0b6ed1615e6b14feb966eef39ece5ebd","tid":697873,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"crazy taxi<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a096461db987898521bbbf0eceab7573ade1f3c4","tid":697873,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"係咪捉精靈？"},{"pid":"84207c70fc15c80589aa70066d710f1949bd5211","tid":697873,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"少少路都行捷徑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4f365162c4fde814a6d9b29f65087750025810","tid":697873,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:30:44.000Z","msg":"的士行樓梯<br />\n揭後語：唔上唔落"},{"pid":"572cd642374ceeebbf73dc21b55797166c872e5b","tid":697873,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾孤鳩map老點？"},{"pid":"5f8c0ec486a6fa791289701f78228ba4976d7da6","tid":697873,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:24:13.000Z","msg":"驗証都市傳說<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次要俾大腳油先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c4b9e511f580b2f5ccd191606191d4fcbe3c7b","tid":697873,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"572cd642374ceeebbf73dc21b55797166c872e5b","tid":697873,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾孤鳩map老點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:08:51.000Z","msg":"見到冇路都照行就唔關古狗事啦"}]}